<item>
            <title>[MATH-1261] Overflow checks in Fraction multiply(int) / divide(int)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MATH-1261</link>
                <project id="12310485" key="MATH">Commons Math</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The member methods multiply(int) / divide(int) in the class org.apache.commons.math3.fraction.Fraction do not have overflow checks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Fraction(numerator * i, denominator);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Fraction(ArithmeticUtils.mulAndCheck(numerator, i), denominator);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;or, considering the case gcd(i, denominator) &amp;gt; 1,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; multiply(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; Fraction(i));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
